Package: RpkgR
Type: Package
Title: R Package Management for Regulated Environments
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Praneethreddy", "Adidela",
      email = "praneethadidela@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for creating and managing local R
    libraries and CRAN-like repositories in regulated
    environments such as SAS Life Science Analytics Framework
    (LSAF). Supports package installation from source,
    dependency resolution, repository validation, repository
    health assessment, installation bundle creation, deployment
    reporting, and reproducible package management workflows for
    regulated analytics.
